USEFUL LINKS:

Spring MVC
https://start.spring.io/  ==> Spring Boot starter
https://spring.io/guides/gs/handling-form-submission/  ==> MVC basics
https://www.baeldung.com/spring-mvc-model-model-map-model-view ==> Model, ModelMap and ModelAndView
https://spring.io/guides/gs/testing-web/ ==> controller testing with mockito
https://memorynotfound.com/unit-test-spring-mvc-rest-service-junit-mockito/ ==> further mockito focussed controller testing
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/18791645/how-to-use-session-attributes-in-spring-mvc ==> session handling

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
RUNNING THE APP WITH GRADLE

BUILD: ./gradlew build
RUN:   java -jar build/libs/incident-report-app-0.1.0.jar   [ie gradle file project name].jar

OR BUILD AND RUN: ./gradlew bootRun
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
RUNNING THE APP WITH MVN

BUILD: ./mvnw clean package
RUN:   java -jar target/gs-handling-form-submission-0.1.0.jar
        [This jar name is set with parameters in the maven script,
        to be equal to the parent directory]

        java -jar target/PostInitialProj-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar

OR BUILD AND RUN: ./mvnw spring-boot:run
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
